WELCOME TO SATISTYPING!
Most commonly used for TIKTOK LIVES.

SHIFT + ENTER :
For special text boxes, will give you a gold border, bigger box and a sound effect.
Can be used for users who send in gifts.

SHIFT + SPACE :
To enable or disable Color mode. Will select a color for each text you will put. 
It will remember the color for each text, and when repeated, will use the same color.

Suggest zooming in 200%, but it depends on your screen.

Enjoy, and thank you for using SATISTYPING!

